If you're making money with Shrike, you owe the copyright holder.

3. Which license applies to me?
-------------------------------

- Running Shrike on your own home network, for your own use? → Non-commercial.
- Using Shrike as part of a paid product or service you sell? → Commercial.
- Unsure? → Contact the copyright holder before deploying to production.

